ou prepare and organize all the necessary documents required for your visa application to ensure completeness and accuracy.\n\n4. **Form Filling Assistance:** Provide support in filling out visa application forms correctly to avoid common mistakes that could lead to delays or rejections.\n\n5. **Interview Preparation:** Offer tips and mock interview sessions to prepare you for visa interviews at embassies or consulates.\n\n6. **Status Tracking:** Assist you in tracking the progress of your visa application and update you on any additional requirements or next steps.\n\n7. **Renewals and Extensions:** Provide guidance on visa renewals, extensions, or changes in visa status.\n\n8. **Appeal and Reapplication Support:** Advise on options and processes if your visa application is denied, including appeal procedures or reapplication strategies.\n\nIf you have a specific visa type or country in mind, I can provide more detailed assistance tailored to that.','delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 09:43:48','2026-03-01 09:43:51','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSRUU1QTVCNEQ5NUVCNDcyQzMwAA==',NULL,NULL),(154,5,'incoming','text','What is your company name','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 09:44:09','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(155,5,'outgoing','text','I am an AI language assistant and do not belong to a company. However, I am here to assist you with any visa-related questions or needs you may have. How can I help you today?','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 09:44:12','2026-03-01 09:44:14','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQzlEODZFOEY0M0U3MzQ3MDI4AA==',NULL,NULL),(156,5,'incoming','text','What are your official emails?','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 09:52:42','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(157,5,'outgoing','text','I don’t have official emails since I’m an AI assistant. However, if you need official contact emails related to a specific visa office