d',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 13:57:34','2026-03-01 13:58:02','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSMzcwOUFGMUY4Mjg2MkZDOTdBAA==',NULL,NULL),(218,5,'incoming','text','Study in korea','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:00:52','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(219,5,'outgoing','text','500 , for more infos check below attachments','sent',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:00:52','2026-03-01 14:00:57','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.6192133926702607,\\\"source\\\":\\\"faq_semantic\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQThFNUE0RDAwQzg0OUM1QzkyAA==',NULL,NULL),(220,5,'outgoing','text','[Attachment]','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:00:52','2026-03-01 14:00:55','\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"document\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/parrotcanada.site\\\\\\/storage\\\\\\/faq_attachments\\\\\\/SS5YJIPtwAHl1ZyKjQCz554HutSaxDAYZHpfQyAk.pdf\\\",\\\"filename\\\":\\\"SS5YJIPtwAHl1ZyKjQCz554HutSaxDAYZHpfQyAk.pdf\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQTNDQTg2MUE1QTczOTk5NDE1AA==',NULL,NULL),(221,5,'incoming','text','Study in USA','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:01:14','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(222,5,'outgoing','text','Great! To study in the USA, you will generally need to obtain an F-1 student visa. Here\'s an overview of the process:\n\n1. **Get Accepted by a SEVP-Approved School**  \n   You must first apply to and be accepted by a Student and Exchange Visitor Program (SEVP)-certified school in the USA. Once accepted, the school will provide you with a Form I-20, which is essential for your visa application.\n\n2. **Pay the SEVIS Fee**  \n   Before your visa interview, you need to pay the SEVIS I-901 fee. This supports the Student and Exchange Visitor Information System (SEVIS).\n\n3. **Complete the DS-160 Visa Application**  \n   Fill out the DS-160 Non-immigrant Visa Application online and print the confirmation page.\n\n4. **Schedule and Prepare for Your Visa Interview**  \n   Book an appointment at the nearest U.S. Embassy or Consulate. Prepare documents including:  \n   - Valid passport  \n   - Form I-20  \n   - DS-160 confirmation page  \n   - SEVIS fee receipt  \n   - Financial documents proving you can support yourself during your studies  \n   - Academic transcripts and standardized test scores (e.g., TOEFL, SAT)  \n   - Proof of ties to your home country (to prove you intend to return after studies)  \n\n5. **Attend the Visa Interview**  \n   During your interview, you will be asked about your study plans, finances, and intentions.\n\n6. **Wait for Visa Processing**  \n   If approved, your visa will be issued within a few days or weeks.\n\nWould you like detailed help with any specific step or information about choosing schools or course programs?','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:01:24','2026-03-01 14:01:26','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSM0FGQkNGMUUzRDVFQjIxNzA0AA==',NULL,NULL),(223,5,'incoming','text','what is the price in canda','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:30:33','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(224,5,'outgoing','text','1000$ and below is attachement','failed',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:30:33','2026-03-01 14:30:37','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"faq_exact\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSNjMxNEMyRDAxNjdGMjY4NjI1AA==',NULL,NULL),(225,5,'outgoing','text','[Attachment]','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:30:33','2026-03-01 14:30:36','\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/parrotcanada.site\\\\\\/storage\\\\\\/faq_attachments\\\\\\/CJD9Q5RA3HAs9rHQlUUMfuo5b6S1d8HRYekv5Ffn.jpg\\\",\\\"filename\\\":\\\"CJD9Q5RA3HAs9rHQlUUMfuo5b6S1d8HRYekv5Ffn.jpg\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQzQ5MEJDMjUyNTExQTYzM0REAA==',NULL,NULL),(226,5,'incoming','text','what is the price in canda','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 14:32:16','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(227,5,'outgoing','text','1000$ and below is attachement','failed',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-