s within Canada  \n- Permanent residence consulting for Canadian immigration programs  \n- Pre-departure briefings and post-arrival settlement support in Canada\n\nTo get started or ask specific questions about moving to Canada, the best way to contact us is by email at infos@visaconsultantcanada.com. We will connect you with a consultant experienced in Canadian immigration and education pathways.\n\nIf you prefer phone contact and are in Africa or Asia, please use our main office numbers; for North America, you can try the Tanzania office phone at +1-438-290-6688.\n\nFeel free to let me know if you have any specific questions about studying, working, or immigrating to Canada!','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:53:12','2026-03-01 16:53:15','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5OTQ0NTcVAgARGBI4OEY4MTMxNEM1MDRDQTJCMTAA',NULL,NULL),(251,5,'incoming','text','study in tanzania','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:58:18','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(252,5,'outgoing','text','If you are interested in studying in Tanzania, our Tanzania office in Dar es Salaam is available to assist you with your educational and visa needs. Here is the relevant information for our Tanzania office:\n\n**Tanzania Office Address:**\nDar Es Salaam Region,  \nUbungo District,  \nWard Mbezi,  \nPostal Code 16113,  \nMbezi Luis, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania\n\n**Contact:**\n- Email: infos@visaconsultantcanada.com  \n- Phone (North America numbers serving Tanzania office): +1-263-588-5750 or +1-438-290-6688\n\nOur team in Tanzania offers in-person consultations to discuss your study plans, university options, and visa requirements. Whether you want guidance on selecting the right Tanzanian universities, student visa application assistance, or help preparing for your studies, we are here to support you.\n\nPlease feel free to reach out to the Tanzania office directly or visit in person to start your education journey in Tanzania.','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:58:22','2026-03-01 16:58:25','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSNzE5RjRCNDE4OUJGRUE3RDRDAA==',NULL,NULL),(253,5,'incoming','text','study in usa','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:58:48','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(254,5,'outgoing','text','The USA is one of our key focus areas. Our global education and immigration expertise covers the USA, and we can guide you through the process of selecting the right university, applying for your student visa (F-1), and preparing for your life as an international student in America. below is fees structure for USA','delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:58:48','2026-03-01 16:58:53','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.6398465723001207,\\\"source\\\":\\\"faq_semantic\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSN0NFQzVFMENGNjM4NDNEOUFEAA==',NULL,NULL),(255,5,'outgoing','text','[Attachment]','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 16:58:48','2026-03-01 16:58:51','\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"document\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/parrotcanada.site\\\\\\/storage\\\\\\/faq_attachments\\\\\\/0cQ5fe2bQkQvsMb05SEkFgeRq3ThsS6xNPqqat9N.pdf\\\",\\\"filename\\\":\\\"0cQ5fe2bQkQvsMb05SEkFgeRq3ThsS6xNPqqat9N.pdf\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSN0VCNDUxRDFEMDhGQjRBNjc3AA==',NULL,NULL),(256,8,'incoming','text','HELLO','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:29:44','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(257,8,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:29:44','2026-03-01 17:29:48','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI3QjdEMDdDNUQ1QTJERkQwOEEA',NULL,NULL),(258,8,'incoming','text','study canada','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:30:02','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(259,8,'outgoing','text','If you\'re interested in studying in Canada, Parrot Canada can assist you with the entire process—from choosing the right university and program to securing your study permit and preparing for your move.\n\nHere’s how we can help you study in Canada:\n\n1. **Initial Eligibility Assessment** – We evaluate your academic background and goals to identify suitable programs and universities.\n2. **University and Program Selection** – We guide you to select programs aligned with your career aspirations.\n3. **Application Assistance** – We support you in preparing and submitting applications to Canadian universities.\n4. **Scholarship Guidance** – We help identify and apply for scholarships to fund your education.\n5. **Study Permit Application** – We assist with the preparation and submission of your Canadian study permit to ensure smooth approval.\n6. **Pre-Departure Briefings** – We prepare you for life in Canada, including what to expect on arrival and how to integrate.\n7. **Post-Arrival Settlement Support** – We help you settle comfortably in Canada with services including accommodation, banking, and community integration.\n\nIf you would like to start with an eligibility assessment or have specific questions about studying in Canada, please let us know! You can also email admission@visaconsultantcanada.com for university admissions and application inquiries.\n\nWould you like detailed information on specific programs, visa requirements, or next steps to begin your application?','delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:30:08','2026-03-01 17:30:10','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI3QTk1RjYyMTc3QUE5REJFOTAA',NULL,NULL),(260,8,'incoming','text','study usa','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:33:13','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(261,8,'outgoing','text','Studying in the USA is an excellent choice for international students seeking high-quality education and diverse academic opportunities. Here\'s how we can assist you in your journey to study in the USA:\n\n1. University and Program Selection  \n- We evaluate your academic background, interests, and career goals to identify suitable universities and programs in the USA.  \n- Through our partnership with 75+ globally recognized universities and 25+ recruitment platforms, we ensure access to a wide range of options across various fields of study.\n\n2. Application Process  \n- We guide you step-by-step in preparing and submitting your university applications, helping you compile necessary documents like transcripts, recommendation letters, and personal statements.  \n- Our expert consultants tailor application strategies to enhance your admission prospects.\n\n3. Student Visa (F-1) Assistance  \n- We provide comprehensive support for your F-1 student visa application, including guidance on document preparation, DS-160 form submission, SEVIS fee payment, and visa interview preparation.  \n- Our close collaboration with authorized university visa experts guarantees updated and accurate visa information.\n\n4. Pre-Departure Preparation  \n- Beyond visas, we offer advice on accommodation, travel planning, health insurance, and cultural adaptation to help you transition smoothly to life in the USA.\n\n5. Fee Structure Transparency  \n- We clearly outline the fee structure for studying in the USA, so you can plan your finances accordingly.\n\nFor detailed inquiries about university admissions or application processes, feel free to contact us at: admission@visaconsultantcanada.com.\n\nLet us help you take the first step toward your American education journey with expert guidance tailored specifically to your profile and goals.','read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:33:19','2026-03-01 17:33:22','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI0QkRFMDRGQ0MyNTMzMjY0QTYA',NULL,NULL),(262,5,'incoming','text','i want to study in usa','received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-01 17:34:57','2026-03-02 14:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(263,5,'outgoing','text','The USA is one of our key focus areas. Our global education and immigration expertise covers the USA, and we ca